#: ../../tips_and_tricks/shooting_tips/shooting_with_your_DSLR.rst:113
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "The White Balance should be set as accurate as possible because DSLRs "
#| "only support 8 bit per color channel (see also my article about the :ref:"
#| "`Waveform Monitor <waveform_and_RGB_parade>`). If done wrong, much of the "
